sub_title: Sales Manager at Vopak I Hydrogen & Ammonia Professional I Vopak Nominee Young Talent award Top vrouw van het Jaar 2022
summary:
Ambitious and progress-driven with a strong interest in the energy sector. 
 • A real team player with excellent communicative skills. 
 • Extensive international experience. 
 • Passionate about techno-economic projects.
 • Keen on programming and modelling.
